fullstack.description:
Offer description We are looking for a Full-Stack JavaScript Developer who is smart, curious, and interested in complex projects. If you have experience with both developing back-and web apps on NestJS and front-end on React then you are a perfect march. As a developer at MindK you will be a part of a strong team where everyone can speak his mind and be heard.
Main tech stack used: Node.js, NestJS, React.js, MUI 5, PostgreSQL, AWS
What we offer:

Competitive salary that matches your qualifications and experience;
Career growth and regular salary reviews;
50% compensation for professional training or conferences;
100% compensation for successfully passing certification;
Free English classes;
Compensation for medical insurance;
An opportunity to participate in conferences and events organised by the company.

If you think we’ll make a great fit — don’t hesitate to send your CV. read more
